{"tid":366514,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好再俾藉口自己","createTime":"2017-08-20T05:40:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-20T06:37:52.000Z","uid":118223,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4f40a6e602f03decccb223942885b911f9e51b36","tid":366514,"uid":118223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T05:40:22.000Z","msg":"由細到大<br />\n你俾過自己幾多次逃避既藉口？<br />\n可能你放棄過自己鐘意既男/女仔<br />\n可能你放棄過自己想讀既科<br />\n可能你放棄過自己既夢想<br />\n為既係各種好現實既原因<br />\n錢,前途,或者只係你覺得根本冇可能成功<br />\n<br />\n但係今次你冇得再退<br />\n你依然可以搵各種藉口<br />\n要返工，怕危險，岀左都冇用...<br />\n岩，你有你既難處<br />\n但係呢啲唔能夠成為你唔去既藉口<br />\n定係你願意為左一日人工<br />\n放棄親手去救返香港既一個機會<br />\n又或者寧願保住一時既安全<br />\n令自己，你未來既子女 更多身邊既人係未來都活係恐懼之下<br />\n岀黎遊行真係未必有用<br />\n但係我深信唔試一定冇用<br />\n<br />\n你已經向現實低頭無數次 俾過自己太多太多藉口<br />\n可能你中學聽左家人話讀左你唔想讀既科<br />\n而家你每日返工都好似煎熬，返工等放工<br />\n可能你最後都冇對佢表白<br />\n而家你愛住一個你唔係真係咁愛既人<br />\n可能你而家發夢 都仲會不時諗起你細個最初既夢想<br />\n但係你已經無辦法去追<br />\n<br />\n如果你想第二時連Winnie the pool都冇權去睇<br />\n如果你甘心到時連通訊軟件都冇得揀 WhatsApp 都冇得用<br />\n如果你可以接受到未來既香港變成人治<br />\n咁你繼續心安理得去返工，坐係公司笑我地呢班傻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只不過如果有一日<br />\n你連動漫都冇得睇<br />\n上咩都要翻牆<br />\n網上講句野都要俾人和諧<br />\n記得唔好抱怨<br />\n因為係你今日自己揀。<br />\n<br />\n我唔同你地講夢想<br />\n唔上升到民族<br />\n單單講為左自己<br />\n你當為左自己又好<br />\n未來既仔女都好<br />\n仲有理由唔企岀黎？<br />\n定係你接受到仔女第二時俾人洗腦式教育<br />\n我就唔得啦。<br />\n<br />\n呢條路好長<br />\n長到見唔到盡頭<br />\n但係點都會有終點<br />\n理得佢有幾遠<br />\n再長既路<br />\n你行一步<br />\n就近一步<br />\n<br />\n仲唔開始行？<br />\n冇得逃避架啦"},{"pid":"c1eb22d544e1a15e23442c715fe0a25ed096e0ce","tid":366514,"uid":116530,"like":2,"dislike":12,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T05:43:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/20/134346_e63547abeeab116d94336ceba53e27d2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F20%2F134346_e63547abeeab116d94336ceba53e27d2.jpg&h=7fb98826&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"24dc119540a46e922214c8f845e967155e1dba28","tid":366514,"uid":35137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T05:45:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/20/134346_e63547abeeab116d94336ceba53e27d2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F20%2F134346_e63547abeeab116d94336ceba53e27d2.jpg&h=7fb98826&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"698b545141c00f088c85ca4244f9b17658520523","tid":366514,"uid":50533,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T05:45:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"20674b67e1e8ee4d0d8617c85c885aab9e3a79e5","tid":366514,"uid":132674,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T05:56:59.000Z","msg":"Do the things you'll regred not doing<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07b5f8d64e4d0e0ce641128da6716e7b66373da1","tid":366514,"uid":104474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T05:59:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔去咪唔去，洗撚藉口</blockquote><br />\n五毛見左你好耐，哩幾日回左有冇上千次？"},{"pid":"e8013e504eaeeb1f913b4984b5668306f9c1f177","tid":366514,"uid":118223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T06:09:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fc1e9686db384aa3fa40d55d91dd1a2c1319bea","tid":366514,"uid":50533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T0